snippet: Psy, the 34-year-old South Korean artist behind the hit, “Gangnam Style,” has even bigger rock ’n’ roll ambitions.
abstract: South Korean artist Psy, behind the hit Gangnam Style, discusses his K-pop genre, his career, and his loftier aspirations now that he is in the spotlight.
lead_paragraph: Psy, the 34-year-old South Korean artist behind the hit, “Gangnam Style,” has even bigger rock ’n’ roll ambitions.
